.description
Another version of Tomas's Life game.  Features include wrapping the screen
as in a torus, independent setting of the horizontal and vertical
resolutions, computing only a specific number of generations, redisplay
only every N generations, a macro language to set up initial generations,
and more.  Works with horizontal resolutions up to 262,112 pixels and
vertical resolutions up to 65,535 pixels.  
